OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading to leave a dry night, with
OL,7,Fvariable cloud and some lengthy clear
OL,8,Fspells. Turning locally chilly, with
OL,9,Fsome patchy fog and rural frost
OL,10,Fforming. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAfter a chilly start, cloud
OL,13,Fwill increase from the south to bring
OL,14,Fsome outbreaks of showery rain during
OL,15,Fthe morning. Locally heavy afternoon
OL,16,Fshowers in the west, eastern areas
OL,17,Fdrier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
