OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarm
OL,6,Fbright spells Saturday, mostly dry. A
OL,7,Fnarrow band of rain moves south on
OL,8,FSunday, with brighter skies following.
OL,9,FSome showers Monday. Often breezy and
OL,10,Ffeeling cooler.
